{"tid":2287302,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【RCEP協定】15國正式簽署協定　各國承諾10年內減至零關稅","createTime":"2020-11-15T15:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T12:21:57.000Z","uid":66087,"like":12,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"c32a69919694ad78a63d5d72a705946c5c7ba34f","tid":2287302,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2803344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2803344&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3jcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=cb7d1367\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2803344</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3ZXcLB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3ZXcLB.jpg&h=805fc936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國、日本、韓國、澳洲、新西蘭、東盟十國在周日（15日）正式簽署區域全面經濟伙伴關係協家（RCEP）。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，參與RCEP的成員國覆蓋22億人口，約佔世界總人口的30%，2019年GDP規模達25.6萬億美元，佔全球經濟總量的29.3%。其中，中國GDP規模14.3萬億美元，佔RCEP成員國的一半以上。<br />\n<br />\n根據協定，各成員之間十年內降至零關稅的承諾為主。其中，中國與日本首次達成雙邊關稅減讓安排，實現歷史性突破。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，目前疫情破壞全球供應鏈的背景下，亞太各國完成RCEP正式簽署，對東亞供應鏈恢復起了極大的利好作用。"},{"pid":"fe80242d10f4cb82275def91a88d19f485f34be2","tid":2287302,"uid":168564,"like":141,"dislike":3,"score":138,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"點睇中國都好鬼着數，其他國家都烚吓烚吓<br />\n到時候比中國平價貨傷害左本土貨就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2037d0c587e983ffcf08a1aa28eb1ded23fd487","tid":2287302,"uid":66087,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"fe80242d10f4cb82275def91a88d19f485f34be2","tid":2287302,"uid":168564,"like":141,"dislike":3,"score":138,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"點睇中國都好鬼着數，其他國家都烚吓烚吓<br />\n到時候比中國平價貨傷害左本土貨就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"成個世界鬼迷心繞比中共控制住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.