","msg":"點睇中國都好鬼着數，其他國家都烚吓烚吓<br />\n到時候比中國平價貨傷害左本土貨就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:11:11.000Z","msg":"如果講關稅唔一定咁講<br />\n大劣人好中意買外國貨, 但進口又真係好撚貴稅<br />\n如果可以低稅入中國賣其實對國貨係好大打擊<br />\n不過唔收稅係一回事, 比唔比你賣又係另一回事<br />\n成班玩左咁耐都未知中共d手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c00a686102a9bb49ac0594adadc509d83559976","tid":2287302,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3faa6fbdd6b7de3ae0cc7d226e6d2b9c2a5f518d","tid":2287302,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"同CCP簽協定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"課金吧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}